<?php
$t = array();
$t[1] = 'Ya ku mut&atilde;ne! Ku bi Ubangijinku da taƙawa Wanda Ya halitta ku daga rai guda, kuma Ya halitta, daga gare shi, ma\'auransa, kuma Ya watsa daga gare su maza m&atilde;su yawa da m&atilde;t&atilde;. Kuma ku bi Allah da taƙawa Wanda kuke r&otilde;ƙon jũna da (sũnan), shi, da kuma zumunta. Lalle ne Allah Ya kasance, a kanku, Mai tsaro ne.';
$t[2] = 'Kuma ku bai wa mar&atilde;yu dũkiy&otilde;yinsu, kuma kada ku musanya mummuna da mai kyau. Kuma kada ku ci dũkiy&otilde;yinsu zuwa ga dũkiy&otilde;yinku. Lalle shi, y&atilde; kasance zunubi ne mai girma.';
$t[3] = 'Kuma idan kun ji ts&otilde;ron b&atilde; z&atilde; ku yi &atilde;dalci ba a cikin mar&atilde;yu, to, (akwai yadda z&atilde; a yi) ku auri abin da ya yi muku d&atilde;ɗi daga m&atilde;t&atilde;; biyu-biyu, da uku-uku, da huɗu-huɗu. Sa\'an nan idan kun ji ts&otilde;ron b&atilde; z&atilde; ku yi &atilde;dalci ba, to, (ku auri) guda ko kuwa abin da hannayenku na dama suka mallaka. Wannan shi ne mafi kusantar zama ba ku wuce haddi ba.';
$t[4] = 'Kuma ku bai wa m&atilde;t&atilde; sad&atilde;k&otilde;kĩnsu da sauƙin b&atilde;yarwa. Sa\'an nan idan suka y&atilde;fe muku wani abu daga gare shi, da d&atilde;ɗin rai, to, ku ci shi da jin d&atilde;ɗi da sauƙin haɗiya.';
$t[5] = 'Kada ku bai wa w&atilde;w&atilde;ye dũkiyarku, wadda Allah Ya sanya ta a gare ku, kun&atilde; m&atilde;su tsayuwa (ga gy&atilde;ranta). Kuma ku ciyar da su a cikinta, kuma ku tuf&atilde;tar da su, kuma ku gaya musu magana sananniya ta alhẽri.';
$t[6] = 'Kuma ku jarraba mar&atilde;yu, har a l&otilde;kacin da suka isa aure. To, idan kun lura da shiriya daga gare su, to, ku mĩƙa musu dũkiy&otilde;yinsu. Kada ku cĩ ta da ɓarna, kuma da gaggawa k&atilde;fin su girma. Kuma wanda yake wad&atilde;tacce, to, ya k&atilde;ma k&atilde;nsa, kuma wanda yake faƙĩri, to, ya ci, gwargwadon yadda ya kamata. To, idan kun mĩƙa musu dũkiy&otilde;yinsu, sai ku shaidar a kansu. Kuma Allah Ya isa Ya zama Mai bincike.';
$t[7] = 'Maza suna da rabo daga abin da iy&atilde;ye biyu da mafi kusantar dangi suka bari, kuma m&atilde;t&atilde; suna da rabo daga abin da iy&atilde;ye biyu da mafi kusantar dangi suka bari, daga abin da ya ƙaranta daga gare shi k&otilde; kuwa ya yi yawa, rabo yankakke.';
$t[8] = 'Kuma idan ma\'abũta zumunta da mar&atilde;yu da matalauta suka halarci rabon, to, ku azurta su daga gare shi, kuma ku faɗa musu magana sananniya ta alhẽri.';
$t[9] = 'Kuma waɗanda suke d&atilde; sun bar zuriyya m&atilde;su rauni a b&atilde;yansu, z&atilde; su ji ts&otilde;ro a kansu, su yi sauna, sa\'an nan su bi Allah da taƙawa, kuma su faɗi magana madaidaiciya.';
$t[10] = 'Lalle ne, waɗanda suke cĩn dũkiyar mar&atilde;yu da z&atilde;lunci, to, wuta kawai suke ci a cikin cikkunansu, kuma za su shiga cikin wata wuta mai tsanani.';
$t[11] = 'Allah Yan&atilde; yi muku wasiyya a cikin \'ya\'yanku; namiji yan&atilde; da rabon m&atilde;t&atilde; biyu. Idan sun kasance m&atilde;t&atilde; ne fiye da biyu kuwa, to, suna da biyu daga kashi uku ɗin abin da ya bari, kuma idan ta zama guda ce (kawai) to, tana da rabi. Kuma iy&atilde;yensa biyu k&otilde;wane ɗaya daga cikinsu yan&atilde; da ɗaya daga kashi shida ɗin abin da ya bari idan wani rẽshe ya kasance gare shi, to, idan rẽshe bai kasance gare shi ba, kuma iy&atilde;yensa ne (kawai) suka g&atilde;je shi, to, uwa tan&atilde; da sulusi (ɗaya daga cikin kashi uku). Sa\'an nan idan \'yan\'uwa sun kasance gare shi, to, uwarsa tana da sudusi (ɗaya daga cikin kashi shida) daga bayan wasiyya wadda ya yi k&otilde; kuwa b&atilde;shi. Ubanninku da \'y&atilde;\'yan ku, ba ku sani ba, wannensu ne mafi kusantar amfani, a gare ku. Yankawa daga Allah. Lalle ne, Allah Y&atilde; kasance Masani Mai hikima.';
$t[12] = 'Kuma kun&atilde; da rabin abin da m&atilde;tanku na aure suka bari idan rẽshe bai kasance gare su ba. Sa\'an nan idan rẽshe ya kasance gare su, to, kun&atilde; da rubu\'i (ɗaya daga cikin kashi huɗu) daga abin da suka barin, daga b&atilde;yan wasiyya wadda suka yi k&otilde; kuma b&atilde;shi. (Sũ) kuma suna da rubu\'i daga abin da kuka bari idan rẽshe bai kasance ba gare ku, idan kuwa rẽshe ya kasance gare ku, to, sun&atilde; da sumuni (ɗaya daga cikin kashi takwas) daga abin da kuka bari, daga b&atilde;yan wasiyya wadda kuka yi k&otilde; kuwa b&atilde;shi. Idan wani namiji ya kasance ana g&atilde;don sa bisa kal&atilde;la, ko kuwa wata mace alh&atilde;li kuwa yana da ɗan\'uwa k&otilde; \'yar\'uwa to, k&otilde;wane ɗaya daga cikinsu yana da sudusi (ɗaya daga cikin kashi shida), sai idan sun kasance mafi yawa daga wannan, to, sũ ab&otilde;kan t&atilde;rayya ne a cikinsulusi (ɗaya bisa uku), daga b&atilde;yan wasiyya wadda aka yi k&otilde; kuma b&atilde;shi. B&atilde; da yana mai cũtarwa ba, ga wasiyya, daga Allah. Kuma Allah Masani ne Mai haƙuri.';
$t[13] = 'Waɗancan iy&atilde;k&otilde;kin Allah ne. Wanda ya yi ɗ&atilde;\'a ga Allah da ManzonSa, (Allah) zai shigar da shi gid&atilde;jen Aljanna (waɗanda) ɗ&otilde;ramu suna gudana daga ƙarƙashinsu, suna madawwama a cikinsu, kuma wannan shi ne rabo babba.';
$t[14] = 'Kuma wanda ya s&atilde;ɓ&atilde; wa Allah da ManzonSa, kuma ya ƙẽtare iy&atilde;k&otilde;kinSa, zai shigarda shi wuta, yana madawwami a cikinta, kuma yana da wata az&atilde;ba mai wal&atilde;kantarwa.';
$t[15] = 'Kuma waɗanda suka je wa alf&atilde;sha daga m&atilde;tanku, to, ku nẽmi Shaidar mut&atilde;ne huɗu daga gare ku a kansu. To, idan sun yi shaida, sai ku tsare su a cikin gid&atilde;je har mutuwa ta karɓi r&atilde;yukansu, ko kuwa Allah Ya sanya wata hanya a gare su.';
$t[16] = 'Kuma waɗanda (maz&atilde; biyu) suka je mata daga ku, to, ku cũtar da su, sa\'an nan idan sun tũba kuma suka kyautata h&atilde;l&atilde;yensu, sai ku kau da kai da ga barinsu. Lalle ne Allah Y&atilde; kasance Mai kaɓar tũba ne, Mai jin ƙai';
$t[17] = 'Abar da take tũba kawai ga Allah, ita ce ga waɗanda suke aikat&atilde;war mugun aiki da j&atilde;hilci sa\'an nan su tũba nan kusa to, waɗannan Allah Yan&atilde; karɓar tũ barsu kuma Allah Y&atilde; kasance Masani ne, Mai hikima.';
$t[18] = 'B&atilde; tũba ba ce ga waɗanda suke aikat&atilde;war mũnanan ayyuka har idan mutuwa ta halarci ɗayansu ya ce: &quot;Lalle ne ni, na tũba yanzu,&quot; kuma b&atilde; tũba ba ce ga waɗanda suke mutuwa alh&atilde;li kuwa sun&atilde; k&atilde;fi rai Waɗannan mun yi musu tattalin wata az&atilde;ba mai raɗaɗi';
$t[19] = 'Ku waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni! B&atilde; ya halatta a gare ku, ku g&atilde;ji m&atilde;t&atilde; a kan tĩlas kuma kadaku hana su aure d&otilde;min ku tafi da s&atilde;shen abin da kuka ba su, f&atilde;ce idan suka zo da wata alf&atilde;sha bayya nanniya kuma ku yi zamantakẽwa da su da alhẽri sa\'an nan idan kun ƙĩ su, to akwai tsamm&atilde;nin ku ƙi wani abu alh&atilde;li kuwa Allah Ya sanya wani alhẽri mai yawaa cikinsa.';
$t[20] = 'Kuma idan kun yi nufin musanya m&atilde;ta a matsayin wata m&atilde;ta, alh&atilde;li kuwa kun bai wa ɗayarsu ƙinɗari to kada ku karɓi k&otilde;me daga gare, shi, shin, z&atilde; ku karɓe shi da ƙarya da zunubi b&atilde;yyananne?';
$t[21] = 'Kuma y&atilde;y&atilde; z&atilde; ku karɓe shi alh&atilde;li kuwa, haƙĩƙa, s&atilde;shenkuy&atilde; s&atilde;du zuwa ga s&atilde;she, kuma sun riƙi alkawari mai kauri daga gare ku?';
$t[22] = 'Kuma kada ku auri abin da ubanninku suka aura daga m&atilde;t&atilde;, f&atilde;ce abin da ya shige. Lalle ne shi, ya kasance alf&atilde;sha da abin ƙy&atilde;ma. Kuma ya mũnana ya zama hanya.';
$t[23] = 'An haramta muku uw&atilde;yenku, da \'y&atilde;\'yanku, da \'yan\'uwanku m&atilde;t&atilde;, da goggonninku, da innoninku, da \'y&atilde;\'yan ɗan\'uwa, da \'ya\'yan \'yar\'uwa, da uw&atilde;yenku waɗanan da suka sh&atilde;yar da ku m&atilde;ma, da \'yan\'uwanku m&atilde;t&atilde; na shan m&atilde;ma, da uw&atilde;yen m&atilde;tanku, da ag&otilde;lolinku waɗanda suke cikin ɗ&atilde;kunanku daga m&atilde;tanku, waɗanda kuka yi duhũli da su, kuma idan ba ku yi duhũli da sũ ba, to, b&atilde;bu laifi a kanku, da m&atilde;tan \'y&atilde;\'yanku waɗanda, suke daga tsatsonku, kuma kada ku haɗa tsakanin \'yan\'uwa biyu m&atilde;t&atilde;, f&atilde;ce abin da ya shige. Lalle ne, Allah Y&atilde; kasance Mai g&atilde;fara ne Mai jin ƙai.';
$t[24] = 'Da tsararrun auren wasu maza, f&atilde;ce dai abin da hannuwanku suka mallaka. (Ku tsare) Litt&atilde;fin Allah a kanku. Kuma an halatta muku abin da yake bayan wancan. Ku nẽma da dukiy&otilde;yinku, kun&atilde; m&atilde;su yin aure, b&atilde; m&atilde;su yin zina ba. sa\'an nan abin da kuka ji daɗi da shi daga gare su, to, ku b&atilde; su ij&atilde;r&otilde;rinsu bisa farillar sad&atilde;ki. B&atilde;bu laifia gare ku ga abin da kuka yi yardatayya da shi a b&atilde;yan farillar sad&atilde;ki. Lalle ne Allah Y&atilde; kasance Masani ne, Mai hikima.';
$t[25] = 'Kuma wanda bai s&atilde;mi wad&atilde;ta ba daga cikinku bisa ga ya auri \'ya\'ya mũminai, to, (ya aura) daga abin da hannuwanku na d&atilde;ma suka mallaka, daga kuyanginku mũminai. Kuma Allah ne Mafi sani ga ĩm&atilde;ninku, s&atilde;shenku daga s&atilde;she. Sai ku aurẽ su da izinin mut&atilde;nensu. Kuma ku b&atilde; su ij&atilde;r&otilde;rinsu bisa ga abin da aka sani, suna m&atilde;su kamun kai b&atilde; m&atilde;su zina ba, kuma b&atilde; m&atilde;su riƙon ab&otilde;kai ba. To, idan aka aure su, sai kuma suka zo da wata alf&atilde;sha, to, akwai a kansu rabin abin da ko a kan, \'ya\'ya daga az&atilde;ba. wancan (auren kuyanga) ga wanda ya ji ts&otilde;ron wahala ne daga gare ku. Kuma ku yi haƙuri shi ne mafi alhẽri a gare ku. Kuma Allah Mai g&atilde;fara ne Mai jin ƙai.';
$t[26] = 'Allah Yan&atilde; nufin Ya bayyana muku, kuma Ya shiryar da ku hany&otilde;yin waɗanda suke a gab&atilde;ninku kuma Ya karɓi tũbarku. Kuma Allah Masani ne Mai hikima.';
$t[27] = 'Kuma Allah Yan&atilde; nufin Ya karɓi tũbarku. Kuma waɗanda suke bin sha\'aw&otilde;yi suna nufin ku karkata, karkata mai girma.';
$t[28] = 'Allah Yana nufin Ya yi muku sauƙi, kuma an halitta mutum yana mai rauni.';
$t[29] = 'Y&atilde; ku waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni! Kada ku ci dũkiy&otilde;yinku a tsak&atilde;ninku da yaudara, f&atilde;ce idan ya kasance, daga fatauci ne, bisa yardatayya daga gare ku. Kuma kada ku kashe k&atilde;nku. Lalle ne Allah Y&atilde; kasance, game da ku, Mai jin ƙai ne.';
$t[30] = 'Wanda ya aikata wancan bisa ta\'adi da z&atilde;lunci, to, z&atilde; Mu ƙ&otilde;ne shi da Wuta. Kuma wannan y&atilde; kasance ga Allah (abu ne) mai sauƙi.';
$t[31] = 'Idan kuka nĩsanci manyan abubuwan da ake hana ku aikat&atilde;wa, to, z&atilde; Mu kankare mũnanan ayyukanku daga gare ku, kuma Mu shigar da ku mashiga ta karimci.';
$t[32] = 'Kuma kada ku yi gurin abin da Allah Ya fifita s&atilde;shenku da shi a kan s&atilde;she; maza suna da rabo daga abin da suka tsirfanta, kuma m&atilde;t&atilde; suna da rabo daga abin da suka tsirfanta. Ku r&otilde;ƙi Allah daga falalarSa. Lalle ne Allah Y&atilde; kasance ga dukkan k&otilde;me, Masani.';
$t[33] = 'Kuma ga k&otilde;wa, Mun sanya magada daga abin da mahaifa da mafiya kusancin zumunta suka bari. Kuma waɗanda rantsuw&otilde;yinku suka ƙulla ku b&atilde; su rabonsu. Lalle ne, Allah Y&atilde; kasance, a kan dukkan k&otilde;me, Mahalarci.';
$t[34] = 'Maza m&atilde;su tsayuwa ne a kan m&atilde;t&atilde;, sab&otilde;da abin da Allah Ya fifita s&atilde;shensu da shi a kan s&atilde;she kuma sab&otilde;da abin da suka ciyar daga dũkiy&otilde;yinsu. To, s&atilde;lihanm&atilde;t&atilde; m&atilde;su ɗ&atilde;\'a ne, m&atilde;su tsarẽwa ga gaibi sab&otilde;da abin da Allah Ya tsare. Kuma waɗanda kuke ts&otilde;ron bijirewarsu, to, ku yi musu gargaɗi, kuma ku ƙaurace musu a cikin wur&atilde;ren kwanciya, kuma ku d&otilde;ke su. Sa\'an nan kuma, idan sun yi muku ɗa\'a, to, kada ku nẽmiwata hanya a kansu. Lalle ne Allah Y&atilde; kasance Maɗaukaki, Mai girma.';
$t[35] = 'Kuma idan kun ji ts&otilde;ron s&atilde;ɓ&atilde;war tsak&atilde;ninsu to ku aika da wani mai sulhu daga mut&atilde;nensa da wani mai sulhu daga mut&atilde;nenta. Idan sun yi nufin gy&atilde;r&atilde;wa, Allah zai daidaita tsak&atilde;ninsu (ma\'auran). Lalle ne Allah Y&atilde; kasance Masani Mai jarrab&atilde;wa.';
$t[36] = 'Kuma ku bauta wa Allah kuma kada ku haɗa wani da Shi, kuma ga mahaifa ku yi kyautat&atilde;wa, kuma ga ma\'abũcin zumunta da mar&atilde;yu da matalauta, da maƙwabci ma\'abũcin kusanta, da maƙwabci manĩsanci, da ab&otilde;ki a gẽfe da ɗan hanya, da abin da hannuwanku na d&atilde;ma suka mallaka. Lalle ne Allah b&atilde; Ya son wanda ya kasance mai t&atilde;ƙama, mai yawan alfahari.';
$t[37] = 'Waɗanda suke yin r&otilde;wa, kuma sun&atilde; umurnin mut&atilde;ne da yin r&otilde;wa, kuma suna ɓ&otilde;yewar abin da Allah Ya b&atilde; su na falalarSa. Kuma Mun yi tattali, sab&otilde;da k&atilde;firai, az&atilde;ba mai wal&atilde;kantarwa.';
$t[38] = 'Kuma waɗanda suke ciyar da dũkiy&otilde;yinsu d&otilde;min nũna wa mut&atilde;ne, kuma b&atilde; su yin ĩm&atilde;ni da Allah, kuma b&atilde; su yin ĩm&atilde;nida R&atilde;nar L&atilde;hira kuma wanda Shaiɗan ya kasance ab&otilde;kin haɗi a gare shi, to, y&atilde; mũnana ga ab&otilde;kinhaɗi.';
$t[39] = 'Kuma mẽne ne a kansu, idan sun yi ĩm&atilde;ni da Allah, kumada R&atilde;nar L&atilde;hira, kuma sun ciyar da abin da Allah Y&atilde; azurt&atilde; su, kuma Allah Ya kasance, gare su, Masani?';
$t[40] = 'Lalle ne, Allah b&atilde; Ya z&atilde;luncin gwargwadon nauyin zarra, idan ta kasance alhẽri ce, zai riɓanya ta, kuma Ya k&atilde;wo daga gunsa ij&atilde;ra mai girma.';
$t[41] = 'To, y&atilde;y&atilde;, idan Mun zo da shaidu daga dukkan al\'umma, kuma Muka zo da kai a kan waɗannan, kana mai shaida!';
$t[42] = 'A r&atilde;nar nan, waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta kuma suka s&atilde;ɓ&atilde; wa Manzo, sun&atilde; gũrin d&atilde; an baje ƙasa dasu, kuma b&atilde; su ɓ&otilde;ye wa Allah wani lab&atilde;ri.';
$t[43] = 'Y&atilde; ku waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni! Kada ku kusanci salla alh&atilde;li kuwa kuna m&atilde;su m&atilde;ye, sai kun san abin da kuke faɗa kuma haka idan kuna m&atilde;su janaba, f&atilde;ce mai ƙẽtare hanya, har ku yi wanka. Kuma idan kun kasance majinyata, ko kuwa a kan tafiya ko kuwa wani daga cikinku, idan ya zo daga k&atilde;shi, k&otilde; kuwa kun sh&atilde;fi m&atilde;t&atilde; ba ku s&atilde;mi ruwa ba, to ku nufi, fuskar ƙasa mai kyau, ku yi sh&atilde;fa ga fuskokinku da hannuwanku. Lalle ne Allah Y&atilde; kasance Mai y&atilde;fẽwa Mai g&atilde;fara.';
$t[44] = 'Shin, ba ka gani ba, zuwa ga waɗanda aka bai wa rabo daga Littafi, suna sayen ɓata, kuma suna nẽman ku ɓace daga hanya?';
$t[45] = 'Kuma Allah ne Mafi sani ga maƙiyanku, kuma Allah Y&atilde; isa Ya zama Majibinci, kuma Y&atilde; isa Ya zama Mataimaki.';
$t[46] = 'Daga waɗanda suka tũba (Yahũdu), akwai wasu sun&atilde; karkatar da magana daga wur&atilde;renta suna cẽwa: &quot;Munjiya kuma mun ƙiya, kuma ka jiya a wani wurin jiy&atilde;wa, kuma r&atilde;\'ina (da ma\'anar \'ruɓaɓɓe\'), ka tsare mu,&quot; d&otilde;min karkatarwa da harsunansu, kuma d&otilde;min sũk&atilde; a cikin addini. Kuma d&atilde; lalle sũ, sun ce: &quot;Mun jiya kuma mun yi ɗa\'a, kuma ka saur&atilde;ra kuma ka d&atilde;kata mana,&quot; haƙĩƙa, d&atilde; ya kasance mafi alhẽri a gare su, kuma mafi daidaita; amma Allah Y&atilde; la\'anẽ su, sab&otilde;da k&atilde;fircinsu don haka b&atilde; z&atilde; su yi ĩm&atilde;ni ba, sai kaɗan.';
$t[47] = 'Y&atilde; kũ waɗanda aka bai wa Litt&atilde;fi! Ku yi ĩm&atilde;ni da abinda Muka saukar, yana mai gaskat&atilde;wa ga abin da yake t&atilde;re da ku, tun gabanin Mu sh&atilde;fe wasu fusk&otilde;ki, sa\'an nan Mu mayar da su a kan b&atilde;yayyakinsu, ko Mu la\'ane su kamar yadda Muka la\'ani masu Asabar. Kuma umurnin Allah ya kasance abin aikat&atilde;wa.';
$t[48] = 'Lalle ne, Allah ba Ya g&atilde;farta a yi shirki game da Shi, kuma Yana g&atilde;farta abin da yake b&atilde;yan wannan ga wanda Yake so, kuma wanda ya yi shirki da Allah, to, lalle ne ya ƙirƙiri zunubi mai girma.';
$t[49] = 'Shin, ba ka gani ba, zuwa ga waɗanda suke tsarkake kansu? &Atilde;\'a, Allah ne Yake tsarkake wanda Yake so. Kuma ba za a zalunce su da zaren gurtsun dabĩno ba.';
$t[50] = 'Ka dũba yadda suke ƙirƙira ƙarya ga Allah! Kuma shi ya isa ga zama zunubi bayyananne.';
$t[51] = 'Shin, ba ka gani ba zuwa ga waɗanda aka bai wa rab&otilde; da ga Littafi suna ĩm&atilde;ni da gunki da Shaiɗan kuma suna cẽwa ga waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta: &quot;Waɗannan ne mafiya shiriya daga waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni ga hanya&quot;?';
$t[52] = 'Waɗannan ne waɗanda Allah Ya la\'ane su, kuma wanda Allah Ya la\'ana to b&atilde; z&atilde; ka s&atilde;mi mataimaki a gare shi ba.';
$t[53] = 'Ko suna da rab&otilde; ne daga mulki? To, a sa\'an nan b&atilde; z&atilde; su iya bai wa mut&atilde;ne hancin gurtsun dabino ba.';
$t[54] = 'Ko suna h&atilde;sadar mut&atilde;ne ne a kan abin da Allah Ya b&atilde; su daga falalarSa? To, lalle ne, Mun bai wa gidan Ibr&atilde;hĩm Litt&atilde;fida hikima kuma Mun b&atilde; su mulki mai girma.';
$t[55] = 'To, daga cikinsu akwai wanda ya yi ĩm&atilde;ni da shi, kuma daga cikinsu akwai wanda ya kange daga gare shi. Kuma y&atilde; isa Jahannama ta hũru da shi.';
$t[56] = 'Lalle ne waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta da ay&otilde;yinMu za Mu ƙ&otilde;ne su da wuta, k&otilde; da yaushe f&atilde;tunsu suka nuna, sai Mu musanya musu wasu f&atilde;tun, d&otilde;min su ɗanɗani az&atilde;ba. Lalle ne Allah Y&atilde; kasance Mabuw&atilde;yi, Mai hikima.';
$t[57] = 'Kuma waɗanda suka yiĩm&atilde;ni, kuma suka aikata ayyuka na ƙwarai, z&atilde; Mu shigar da su gid&atilde;jen Aljanna, (waɗanda) ƙ&otilde;ramu sun&atilde; gud&atilde;na daga ƙarƙashinsu, sun&atilde; dawwamammu a cikinsu har abada suna da, a cikinsu, m&atilde;tan aure m&atilde;su tsarki, Kuma Mun&atilde; shigar da su a wata inuwa matabbaciyar lumshi.';
$t[58] = 'Lalle ne Allah Yan&atilde; umurnin ku ku b&atilde;yar da am&atilde;n&otilde;ni zuwa ga m&atilde;su sũ. Kuma idan kun yi hukunci a tsak&atilde;nin mut&atilde;ne, ku yi hukunci da &atilde;dalci. Lalle ne Allah m&atilde;dalla da abin da Yake yi muku wa\'azi da shi. Lalle ne Allah Y&atilde; kasance Mai ji ne, Mai gani.';
$t[59] = 'Y&atilde; kũ waɗanda suka yiĩm&atilde;ni! Ku yi ɗ&atilde;\'a ga Allah, kuma ku yi ɗ&atilde;\'a ga ManzonSa, da ma\'abũta al\'amari daga cikinku. Idan kun yi j&atilde;yayya a cikin wani abu, to ku mayar da shi zuwa ga Allah da ManzonSa idan kun kasance kun&atilde; ĩm&atilde;ni da Allah da R&atilde;nar L&atilde;hira. wannan ne mafi alhẽri, kuma mafi kyau ga fassara.';
$t[60] = 'Shin, ba ka gani ba, zuwa ga waɗanda suke riy&atilde;war cẽwa sun&atilde; ĩm&atilde;ni da abin da aka saukar zuwa gare ka da abin da aka saukar daga gab&atilde;ninka, sun&atilde; nufin su kai ƙ&atilde;ra zuwa ga &brvbar;&atilde;gũtu alh&atilde;li kuwa, lalle ne, an umurce su da su k&atilde;firta da shi, kuma Shaiɗan yan&atilde; nẽman ya ɓatar da su, ɓatarwa mai nĩsa.';
$t[61] = 'Kuma idan aka ce musu: &quot;Ku zo zuwa ga abin da Allah Ya saukar, kuma zuwa ga Manzo&quot; z&atilde; ka ga mun&atilde;fukai sun&atilde; kange mut&atilde;ne daga gare ka, kangẽwa.';
$t[62] = 'To, yaya, idan wata masĩfa ta s&atilde;me su, sab&otilde;da abin da hannuwansu suka gab&atilde;tar sa\'an nan kuma su je maka sun&atilde; rantsuwa da Allah cẽwa, &quot;Ba mu yi nufin k&otilde;me ba sai kyautatawa da daidait&atilde;wa.&quot;?';
$t[63] = 'Waɗannan ne waɗanda Allah Ya san abin da ke cikin zuk&atilde;tansu. Sab&otilde;da haka ka kau da kai daga gare su, kuma ka yi musu gargaɗi, kuma ka gaya musu, a cikin sha\'anin kansu, magana mai nauyi da fas&atilde;ha.';
$t[64] = 'Kuma ba Mu aiki wani Manzo ba f&atilde;ce d&otilde;min a yi masa ɗ&atilde;\'a da izinin Allah. Kuma d&atilde; dai lalle sũ a l&otilde;kacin da suka z&atilde;lunci kansu, sun zo maka sa\'an nan suka nẽmi g&atilde;farar Allah kuma Manzo ya nẽma musu g&atilde;fara, haƙĩƙa, d&atilde; sun s&atilde;mi Allah Mai karɓar tũba Mai jin ƙai.';
$t[65] = 'To, a\'aha! Ina rantsuwa da Ubangijinka, ba za su yi ĩm&atilde;ni ba, sai sun yarda da hukuncinka ga abin da ya s&atilde;ɓa a tsak&atilde;ninsu, sa\'an nan kuma ba su s&atilde;mi wani ƙunci a cikin zuk&atilde;tansu ba, daga abin da ka hukunta, kuma su sallama sallam&atilde;wa.';
$t[66] = 'Kuma d&atilde; dai lalle Mũ, Mun wajabta musu cẽwa, &quot;Ku kashe kanku, ko kuwa ku, fita daga gid&atilde;jenku,&quot; d&atilde; ba su aikata shi ba, f&atilde;ce kaɗan daga gare su. Kuma d&atilde; dai lalle sũ sun aikata abin da ake yi musu gargaɗi da shi, haƙĩƙa, d&atilde; y&atilde; kasance mafi alhẽri dagagare su, kuma mafi tsanani ga tabbatarwa.';
$t[67] = 'Kuma a sa\'an nan, haƙĩƙa, d&atilde; Mun b&atilde; su, l&atilde;da mai girma, daga gunMu.';
$t[68] = 'Kuma lalle ne, d&atilde; Mun shiryar da su hanya madaidaiciya.';
$t[69] = 'Kuma waɗannan da suka yi ɗ&atilde;\'a ga Allah da Mazonsa, to, waɗannan sun&atilde; t&atilde;re da waɗanda Allah Ya yi ni\'ima a kansu, daga annab&atilde;wa da m&atilde;su yawan gaskat&atilde;wa, da masu shah&atilde;da da s&atilde;lihai. kuma waɗannan sun kyautatu ga zama ab&otilde;kan tafiya.';
$t[70] = 'Waccan falalar daga Allah take, kuma Allah Y&atilde; isa zama Masani.';
$t[71] = 'Y&atilde; kũ waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni! Ku riƙi shirinku sa\'an nan ku fitar da hari jama\'a, jama\'a ko ku fitar da yaƙi gaba ɗaya.';
$t[72] = 'Kuma lalle ne daga cikinku akwai mai f&atilde;sarwa. To idan wata masĩfa ta s&atilde;me ku, sai ya ce: &quot;Lalle ne, Allah Ya yi mini ni\'ima d&otilde;min ban kasance mahalarci t&atilde;re da su ba.&quot;';
$t[73] = 'Kuma lalle ne idan wata falala daga Allah ta s&atilde;me ku haƙĩƙa, tabbas, yan&atilde; cẽwa, kamar wata s&otilde;yayya ba ta kasance a tsak&atilde;ninku da shi ba: &quot;Y&atilde; kaitona! D&atilde; na zama t&atilde;re da su dai, d&otilde;min in rabonta da rab&otilde; mai girma!&quot;';
$t[74] = 'Sai waɗanda suke sayar da rayuwar dũniya su karɓi ta L&atilde;hira su yi y&atilde;ƙi, a cikin hanyar Allah. Kuma wanda ya yi y&atilde;ki a cikin hanyar Allah to a kashe shi ko kuwa ya rinj&atilde;ya, sa\'an nan z&atilde; Mu ba shi ij&atilde;ra mai girma.';
$t[75] = 'Kuma mẽne ne ya s&atilde;me ku, b&atilde; ku yin y&atilde;ƙi a cikin hanyar Allah, da waɗanda aka raunanar daga maza da mata da y&atilde;ra sun&atilde; cewa: &quot;Y&atilde; Ubangijinmu! Ka fitar da mu daga wannan alƙarya wadda mut&atilde;nenta suke da z&atilde;lunci, kuma Ka sanya mana majiɓinci daga gunKa, kuma Ka sanya mana mataimaki daga gunKa.&quot;?';
$t[76] = 'Waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni, sun&atilde; y&atilde;ki a cikin hanyar Allah, kuma waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta sun&atilde; y&atilde;ƙi a cikin hanyar &brvbar;&atilde;gũtu (Shaiɗan). To, ku y&atilde;ƙi majiɓintan Shaiɗan. Lalle ne kaidin Shaiɗan y&atilde; kasance mai rauni.';
$t[77] = 'Shin, ba ka gani ba zuwa ga waɗanda aka ce musu: &quot;Ku kange hannuwanku, kuma ku tsayar da salla, kuma ku b&atilde;yar da zakka.&quot;? To a l&otilde;kacin da aka wajabta musu y&atilde;ƙi sai ga wani ɓangare daga cikinsu sun&atilde; ts&otilde;ron mut&atilde;ne kamar ts&otilde;ron Allah k&otilde; kuwa mafi tsanani ga ts&otilde;ron, kuma suka ce: &quot;Ya Ubangijinmu! Don me Ka wajabta y&atilde;ƙi a kanmu? Me ya hana Ka jinkirta mana zuwa ga wani ajali na kusa?&quot;Ka ce: &quot;Jin d&atilde;ɗin dũniya kaɗan ne, kuma L&atilde;hira ce mafi alhẽri ga wanda ya yi taƙawa. Kuma b&atilde; a z&atilde;luntar ku da sĩlĩlin hancin gurtsun dabĩno!';
$t[78] = '&quot;Inda duk kuka kasance, mutuwa z&atilde; ta riske ku, kuma k&otilde; da kun kasance ne a cikin g&atilde;nuw&otilde;yi ing&atilde;tattu!&quot;Kuma idan wani alhẽri ya s&atilde;me su sai su ce: &quot;Wannan daga wurin Allah ne,&quot; kuma idan wata cũta ta s&atilde;me su, sai su ce: &quot;Wannan daga gare ka ne.&quot;Ka ce: &quot;Dukkansu daga Allah ne.&quot; To, me ya s&atilde;mi waɗannan mut&atilde;ne, b&atilde; su kusantar fahimtar magana?';
$t[79] = 'Abin da ya s&atilde;me ka daga alhẽri, to, daga Allah yake, kuma abin da ya s&atilde;me ka daga sharri, to, daga kanka yake, kuma Mun aike ka zuwa ga mut&atilde;ne, (kana) Manzo, kuma Allah Y&atilde; isa ga zama shaida.';
$t[80] = 'Wanda ya yi ɗ&atilde;\'a ga Manzo, to, haƙĩƙa, y&atilde; yi ɗ&atilde;\'a ga Allah. Kuma wanda ya jũya b&atilde;ya, to, ba Mu aike ka ba don ka zama mai tsaro a kansu.';
$t[81] = 'Kuma sun&atilde; cẽwa, &quot;D&atilde;\'a&quot; sa\'an nan idan sun fita daga wurinka, sai wata ƙungiya daga cikinsu ta kw&atilde;na da niyyar wanin abin da take faɗa, alh&atilde;li kuwa Allah na rubũta abin da suke kw&atilde;na da niyyarsa. Sab&otilde;da haka ka kau da kai daga gare su, kuma ka d&otilde;gara ga Allah, kuma Allah Y&atilde; isa ya zama wakĩli.';
$t[82] = 'Shin, b&atilde; su kula da Alƙur\'&atilde;ni, kuma d&atilde; y&atilde; kasance daga wurin wanin Allah haƙĩƙa, d&atilde; sun s&atilde;mu, a cikinsa, s&atilde;ɓ&atilde; wa jũnamai yawa?';
$t[83] = 'Kuma idan wani al\'amari daga aminci ko ts&otilde;ro ya je musu, sai su w&atilde;tsa shi. D&atilde; sun mayar da shi zuwa ga Manzo da ma\'abũta al\'amari daga gare su, lalle ne, waɗanda suke yin bincikensa, daga gare su, z&atilde; su san shi. Kuma b&atilde; d&otilde;min falalar Allah b&atilde; a kanku da rahamarSa, haƙĩƙa, d&atilde; kun bi Shaiɗan f&atilde;ce kaɗan.';
$t[84] = 'Sab&otilde;da haka, ka yi y&atilde;ƙi a cikin hanyar Allah, ba a kallafa maka ba, face a kanka, kuma ka kwaɗaitar da mũminai. Akwai tsamm&atilde;nin Allah Ya kange g&atilde;fin waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta, kuma Allah ne Mafi tsananin g&atilde;fi, kuma Mafi tsananin azabt&atilde;wa.';
$t[85] = 'Wanda ya yi cẽto, cẽto mai kyau, zai s&atilde;mi rabo daga gare shi, kuma wanda ya yi cẽto, cẽto mummũna, zai s&atilde;mi ma\'aunidaga gare shi, Kuma Allah Y&atilde; kasance, a kan dukkan k&otilde;me, Mai ƙayyade l&otilde;kaci.';
$t[86] = 'Kuma idan an gaishe ku da wata gaisuwa, to, ku yi gaisuwa da abin da yake mafi kyau daga gare ta, k&otilde; kuwa ku mayar da ita. Kuma Allah Y&atilde; kasance a kan dukkan k&otilde;me Mai liss&atilde;fi.';
$t[87] = 'Allah b&atilde;bu abin bautawa face Shi. Lalle ne haƙĩƙa Yana t&atilde;ra ku har zuwa ga Yinin &iexcl;iy&atilde;ma b&atilde;bu shakka a cikinsa. Kuma w&atilde;ne ne mafi gaskiya daga Allah ga 1&atilde;b&atilde;ri.';
$t[88] = 'To, mẽne ne ya s&atilde;me ku a cikin mun&atilde;fukai kun zama ƙungiya biyu, alh&atilde;li kuwa Allah ne Ya mayar da su sab&otilde;da abin da suka tsirfanta? Shin, kun&atilde; nufin ku shiryar da wanda Allah Ya ɓatar ne? Kuma wanda Allah Ya ɓatar to b&atilde; z&atilde; ka s&atilde;mi wata hanya ba zuwa gare shi.';
$t[89] = 'Suna gũrin ku k&atilde;firta kamar yadda suka k&atilde;firta, d&otilde;min ku kasance daidai. Sab&otilde;da haka kada ku riƙi wasu mas&otilde;ya daga cikinsu, sai sun y&otilde; hijira a cikin hanyar Allah. Sa\'an nan idan sun jũya, to, ku k&atilde;m&atilde; su kuma ku kashe su inda duk kuka s&atilde;me su. Kuma kada ku riƙi wani mas&otilde;yi daga gare su ko wani mataimaki.';
$t[90] = 'F&atilde;ce dai waɗanda suke s&atilde;duwa zuwa ga wasu mut&atilde;ne waɗanda a tsak&atilde;ninku da su akwai alkawari, k&otilde; kuwa waɗanda suke sun je muku (domin) ƙir&atilde;zansu sun yi ƙunci ga su y&atilde;ke ku, k&otilde; su y&atilde;ƙi mut&atilde;nensu. Kuma d&atilde; Allah Y&atilde; so lalle ne, d&atilde; Y&atilde; b&atilde; su ĩko a kanku, sa\'an nan, haƙĩka, su y&atilde;ke ku. To, idan sun nĩsance ku sa\'an nan ba su y&atilde;ƙe ku ba, kuma suka jẽfa sulhu zuwa gare ku, to, Allah bai sanya wata hanya ba, a gare ku, a kansu.';
$t[91] = 'Za ku s&atilde;mi wasu sun&atilde; nufin su amintar da ku kuma su amintar da mut&atilde;nensu, k&otilde; da yaushe aka mayar da su ga fitina, sai a dulmuy&atilde; su a cikinta. To, idan ba su nĩsance ku ba, kuma sun jẽfa sulhu zuwa gare ku, kuma sun kange hannuwansu, to, ku k&atilde;m&atilde; su, kuma ku kashe su inda duk kuka k&atilde;m&atilde; su, kuma waɗannan, Mun sanya muku dalĩli bayyanannea kansu.';
$t[92] = 'Kuma b&atilde; ya kasancẽwa ga mũmini ya kashe wani mũmini, f&atilde;ce bisa ga kuskure. Kuma wanda ya kashe mũmini bisa ga kuskure, sai ya \'yanta wuya mũmina tare da mĩƙa diyya ga mut&atilde;nensa, &atilde;ce idan sun bari sadaka. Sa\'an nan idan (wanda aka kashe) ya kasance daga wasu mut&atilde;ne maƙiya a gare ku, kuma shi mũminine, sai ya \'yanta wuya mũmina. Kuma idan ya kasance daga wasu mut&atilde;ne ne (waɗanda) a tsak&atilde;ninku da tsak&atilde;ninsu akwai alkawari, sai ya b&atilde;yar da diyya ga mut&atilde;nensa, tare da \'yanta wuya mũmina. To, wanda bai s&atilde;mi (wuyan ba) sai azumin watanni biyu jẽre, d&otilde;min tũba daga Allah. Kuma Allah Y&atilde; kasance Masani, Mai hikima.';
$t[93] = 'Kuma wanda ya kashe wani mũmini da ganganci, to, sakamakonsa Jahannama, yana madawwami a cikinta kuma Allah Y&atilde; yi fushi a kansa, kuma Ya la\'ane shi, kuma Ya yi masa tattalin az&atilde;ba mai girma.';
$t[94] = 'Y&atilde; kũ waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni! Idan kun yi tafiya (a cikin ƙasa), d&otilde;min jih&atilde;di, to, ku nẽmi b&atilde;yani. Kuma kada ku ce wa wanda ya jĩfa sallama zuwa gare ku: &quot;B&atilde; Musulmi kake ba.&quot; Kun&atilde; nẽman h&atilde;jar r&atilde;yuwar dũniya, to, a wurin Allah akwai ganim&otilde;mi m&atilde;su yawa. Kamar wannan ne kuka kasance a gab&atilde;nin ku musulunta, sa\'an nan Allah Ya yi muku falala. Sab&otilde;da haka ku zan nẽman bay&atilde;ni. Lalle ne Allah Y&atilde; kasance, ga abin da kuke aikat&atilde;wa, Masani.';
$t[95] = 'M&atilde;su zama daga barin y&atilde;ƙi daga mũminai, wasun ma\'abũta larũra da m&atilde;su jih&atilde;di a cikin hanyar Allah da dũkiy&otilde;yinsu da r&atilde;yukansu, b&atilde; su zama daidai. Allah Y&atilde; fĩfĩta m&atilde;su jih&atilde;di da dũkiyoyinsu da r&atilde;yukansu a kan m&atilde;su zama, ga daraja. Kuma dukansu Allah Y&atilde; yi musu alkawari da abu mai kyau. Kuma Allah y&atilde; fĩfĩta m&atilde;su jih&atilde;di a kan m&atilde;su zama da l&atilde;da mai girma.';
$t[96] = 'Daraj&otilde;ji daga gare Shi da g&atilde;fara da rahama. Kuma Allah Y&atilde; kasance Mai g&atilde;fara ne, Mai jin ƙai.';
$t[97] = 'Lalle ne, waɗanda mal&atilde;\'ĩku suka karɓi r&atilde;yukansu, (alh&atilde;li) sun&atilde; m&atilde;su z&atilde;luntar kansu, sun ce (musu): &quot;A cikin me kuka kasance?&quot; (Su kuma) suka ce: &quot;Mun kasance waɗanda aka raunana a cikin ƙasa.&quot; Suka ce: &quot;Ashe ƙasar Allah ba ta kasance mayalwaciya ba, d&otilde;min ku yi hijira a cikinta?&quot; To, waɗannan mak&otilde;marsu Jahannama ce. Kuma t&atilde; mũnana ta zama mak&otilde;ma.';
$t[98] = 'F&atilde;ce waɗanda aka raunana daga maza da m&atilde;t&atilde; da y&atilde;ra waɗanda b&atilde; su iya yin wata dab&atilde;ra, kuma b&atilde; su shiryuwa ga hanya.';
$t[99] = 'To, waɗannan akwai tsamm&atilde;nin Allah Ya y&atilde;fe laifi daga gare su, kuma Allah Y&atilde; kasance Mai y&atilde;fẽwa ne, Mai g&atilde;fara.';
$t[100] = 'Kuma wanda ya yi hijira a cikin hanyar Allah, zai s&atilde;mu, a cikin ƙasa, wur&atilde;ren jũy&atilde;wa m&atilde;su yawa da yalwa. Kuma wanda ya fita daga gidansa yana mai hijira zuwa ga Allah da ManzonSa, sa\'an nan kuma mutuwa ta riske shi, to, lalle ne, l&atilde;darsa t&atilde; auku ga Allah, Kuma Allah Y&atilde; kasance, a gare ku, Mai g&atilde;fara, Mai jin ƙai.';
$t[101] = 'Kuma idan kun yi tafiya a cikin ƙasa to, b&atilde;bu laifi a kanku ku rage daga salla idan kun ji ts&otilde;ron waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta su fitine ku. Lalle ne k&atilde;firai sun kasance, a gare ku, maƙiyi bayyananne.';
$t[102] = 'Kuma idan k&atilde; kasance a cikinsu, sai ka tsayar musu da salla, to, wata ƙungiya daga gare su ta tsaya t&atilde;re da kai, kuma sai su riƙe mak&atilde;mansu. Sa\'an nan idan sun yi salla, to, sai su kasance daga b&atilde;yanku. Kuma wata ƙungiya ta dabam (ta) waɗanda ba su yi sallar ba, ta zo, sa\'an nan su yi sallar t&atilde;re da kai. Kuma su riƙi shirinsu da mak&atilde;mansu. Waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta sun yi gũrin d&atilde; dai kuna shagala daga makamanku da k&atilde;yanku d&otilde;min su karkata a kanku, karkata guda. Kuma b&atilde;bu laifi, a kanku idan wata cũta daga ruwan sama ta kasance a gare ku, k&otilde; kuwa kun kasance m&atilde;su jinya ga ku ajiye mak&atilde;manku kuma dai ku riƙi shirinku. Lalle ne, Allah Y&atilde; yi tattali, ga k&atilde;firai, az&atilde;ba mai walakantarwa.';
$t[103] = 'Sa\'an nan idan kun ƙ&atilde;re salla, to ku ambaci Allah tsaye da zaune da a kan s&atilde;sanninku. Sa\'an nan idan kun natsu, to, ku tsayar da Salla. Lalle ne salla t&atilde; kasance a kan mũminai, farilla mai ƙayyadaddun l&otilde;kuta.';
$t[104] = 'Kuma kada ku sassauta a cikin nẽman mut&atilde;nen idankun kasance kuna jin z&otilde;gi, to, lalle sũ ma, suna jin z&otilde;gi kamar yadda kuke jin z&otilde;gi. Kuma kuna tsamm&atilde;ni, daga Allah, abin da b&atilde; su tsamm&atilde;ni. Kuma Allah Y&atilde; kasance Masani Mai hikima.';
$t[105] = 'Lalle ne, Mũ, Mun saukar, zuwa gare ka, Litt&atilde;fi da gaskiya, d&otilde;min ka yi hukunci a tsak&atilde;nin mut&atilde;ne da abin da Allah Ya nũna maka, kuma kada ka kasance mai husũma d&otilde;min m&atilde;su yaudara.';
$t[106] = 'Kuma ka nẽmi Allah g&atilde;fara. Lalle ne Allah Y&atilde; kasance Mai g&atilde;fara, Mai jin ƙai.';
$t[107] = 'Kuma kada ka yi j&atilde;yayya d&otilde;min tunkuɗe wa waɗanda suka yaudari kansu. Lalle ne Allah ba Ya son wanda ya kasance mai yawan h&atilde;\'inci mai yawan zunubi.';
$t[108] = 'Suna nẽman ɓ&otilde;yewa daga mut&atilde;ne kuma b&atilde; su nẽmanɓ&otilde;yewa daga Allah, alh&atilde;li kuwa Shi Yana t&atilde;re da su a l&otilde;kacin da suke kw&atilde;na da niyyar yin abin da b&atilde; Ya yarda da shi daga maganar. Kuma Allah Y&atilde; kasance ga abin da suke aikat&atilde;wa Mai kẽwayẽwa.';
$t[109] = 'G&atilde; ku, y&atilde; waɗannan! Kun yi jid&atilde;li, d&otilde;min tunkuɗe musu (kunya) a cikin r&atilde;yuwar dũniya, to, wane ne zai yi jidali domin tunkuɗe musu a R&atilde;nar &iexcl;iy&atilde;ma? Ko kuwa w&atilde;ne ne zai kasance wakĩli a kansu?';
$t[110] = 'Kuma wanda ya aikata cũta k&otilde; kuwa ya z&atilde;lunci kansa, sa\'an nan kuma ya nẽmi Allah g&atilde;fara, zai s&atilde;mi Allah Mai g&atilde;fara, Mai jin ƙai.';
$t[111] = 'Kuma wanda ya yi tsirfanci zunubi, to yan&atilde; tsirfarsa ne a kan kansa kawai. Kuma Allah Y&atilde; kasance Masani, Mai hikima.';
$t[112] = 'Kuma wanda ya yi tsiwirwirin kuskure ko kuwa zunubi sa\'an nan kuma ya jẽfi wani barrantacce da shi, to, lalle ne y&atilde; tattali ƙirƙiren ƙarya da zunubi bayyananne.';
$t[113] = 'Kuma b&atilde; d&otilde;min falalar Allah ba, a kanka, da rahamarSa, haƙĩƙa, d&atilde; wata ƙungiya daga gare su ta himmatu ga su ɓatar da kai. Kuma b&atilde; su ɓatarwa f&atilde;ce kansu, kuma b&atilde; su cũtar ka daga k&otilde;me, Kuma Allah Y&atilde; saukar da Litt&atilde;fi da hikima gare ka, kuma Ya sanar da kai abin da ba ka kasance k&atilde; sani ba. Kuma falalar Allah t&atilde; kasance mai girma a gare ka.';
$t[114] = 'B&atilde;bu wani alhẽri a cikin m&atilde;su yawa daga g&atilde;nawarsu f&atilde;ce wanda ya yi umurni da wata sadaka k&otilde; kuwa wani alhẽri k&otilde; kuwa gy&atilde;ra a tsak&atilde;nin mut&atilde;ne. Wanda ya aikata haka d&otilde;min nẽman yard&otilde;din Allah to z&atilde; Mu b&atilde; shi l&atilde;da mai girma.';
$t[115] = 'Kuma wanda ya s&atilde;ɓ&atilde; wa Manzo daga b&atilde;yan shiriya t&atilde; bayyana a gare shi, kuma ya bi wanin hanyar mũminai, z&atilde; Mu jiɓintar masa abin da ya jiɓinta, kuma Mu ƙ&otilde;ne shi da Jahannama. Kuma t&atilde; mũnana ta zama mak&otilde;ma.';
$t[116] = 'Lalle ne, Allah ba Ya g&atilde;farta a yi shirki da Shi, kuma Yana g&atilde;farta abin da yake b&atilde;yan wannan, ga wanda Yake so. Kuma wanda ya yi shirki da Allah, to, lalle ne ya ɓace ɓata mai nĩsa.';
$t[117] = 'B&atilde; su kiran k&otilde;wa, baicin Shi, f&atilde;ce m&atilde;t&atilde; kuma b&atilde; su kiran k&otilde;wa f&atilde;ce Shaiɗan, mai tsaurin kai.';
$t[118] = 'Allah Y&atilde; la\'ane shi. Kuma ya ce: &quot;Lalle ne, z&atilde; ni riƙi rab&otilde; yankakke, daga b&atilde;yinKa.';
$t[119] = '&quot;Kuma lalle ne, in&atilde; ɓatar da su, kuma lalle ne in&atilde; sanya musu gũri, kuma lalle ne ina umurnin su d&otilde;min su k&atilde;tse kunnuwan dabb&otilde;bi, kuma lalle ne in&atilde; umurnin su d&otilde;min su canza halittar Allah.&quot; Kuma wanda ya riƙi Shaiɗan majiɓinci, baicin Allah, to, haƙĩƙa y&atilde; yi hasara, hasara bayyananniya.';
$t[120] = 'Yan&atilde; yi musu alkawari, kuma yan&atilde; sanya musu gũri, alh&atilde;li Shaiɗan b&atilde; ya yi musu wani wa\'adĩn k&otilde;me face ruɗi.';
$t[121] = 'Waɗannan matattararsu Jahannama ce, kuma b&atilde; s&atilde;mun makarkata daga gare ta.';
$t[122] = 'Kuma waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni, kuma suka aikata ayyukan ƙwarai, z&atilde; mu shigar da su gid&atilde;jen Aljanna (waɗanda) ƙ&otilde;ramu sun&atilde; gud&atilde;na a ƙarƙashinsu, sun&atilde; m&atilde;su dawwama a cikinsu har abada bisa ga wa\'adin Allah tabbatacce. W&atilde;ne ne mafi gaskiya daga Allah ga magana?';
$t[123] = '(Al\'amari) bai zama gũrace- gũracenku ba, kuma ba gũrace- gũracen Mut&atilde;nen Litt&atilde;fi ba ne. Wanda ya aikata mummunan aiki z&atilde; a s&atilde;ka masa da shi kuma b&atilde; zai s&atilde;mi wani mas&otilde;yi ba, baicin Allah, kuma b&atilde; zai s&atilde;mi mataimaki ba.';
$t[124] = 'Kuma wanda ya yi aiki daga ayyukan ƙwarai, namiji ne ko kuwa mace, alh&atilde;li kuwa Yan&atilde; mũmini, to, waɗannan sun&atilde; shiga Aljanna kuma b&atilde; z&atilde; a z&atilde;lunce su da gwargwadon hancin gurtsun dabĩ no ba.';
$t[125] = 'Kuma w&atilde;ne ne ya fi kyau ga addini daga wanda ya sallama fuskarsa ga Allah, alh&atilde;li kuwa yan&atilde; mai kyautatawa kuma ya bi aƙidar Ibr&atilde;hĩm, Yan&atilde; mai karkata zuwa ga gaskiya? Allah Y&atilde; riƙi Ibr&atilde;hĩm bad&atilde;ɗayi.';
$t[126] = 'Kuma Allah ke da (mallakar) abin da ke cikin sammai da kuma abin da ke cikin ƙasa kuma Allah Y&atilde; kasance, a dukkan, k&otilde;me, Mai kẽwayewa.';
$t[127] = 'Sun&atilde; yi maka fatawa a cikin sha\'anin m&atilde;t&atilde;. Ka ce: &quot;Allah Yan&atilde; bayyana fatawarku a cikin sha\'aninsu, da abin da ake karant&atilde;wa a kanku a cikin Litt&atilde;fi, a cikin sha\'anin mar&atilde;yun m&atilde;t&atilde; waɗanda ba ku b&atilde; su abin da aka rubũta musu (na g&atilde;do) ba, kuma kun&atilde; kwaɗayin ku aurẽ su, da sha\'anin waɗanda aka raunana daga y&atilde;ra, da sha\'anin tsayuwarku ga mar&atilde;yu da &atilde;dalci. Kuma abin da kuka aikata daga alhẽri, to, lalle ne, Allah Y&atilde; kasance Masani a gare shi.&quot;';
$t[128] = 'Kuma idan wata mace ta ji ts&otilde;ron ƙiyo daga mijinta k&otilde; kuwa bijirẽwa to, b&atilde;bu laifi a kansu su yi sulhu a tsak&atilde;ninsu, sulhu (mai kyau) Kuma yin sulhu ne mafi alhẽri. Kuma an halartar wa rayũka yin r&otilde;wa. Kuma idan kun kyautata, kuma kuka yi taƙawa, to, lalle ne, Allah Y&atilde; kasance, ga abin da kuke aikat&atilde;wa, Masani.';
$t[129] = 'Kuma b&atilde; z&atilde; ku iya yin &atilde;dalci ba a tsakanin m&atilde;t&atilde; k&otilde; d&atilde; kun yi kwaɗayin yi. Sab&otilde;da haka kada ku karkata, dukan karkata, har ku bar ta kamar wadda aka r&atilde;taye. Kuma idan kun yi sulhu, kuma kuka yi taƙawa, to, lalle ne Allah Y&atilde; kasance Mai g&atilde;fara, Mai jin ƙai.';
$t[130] = 'Kuma idan sun rabu, Allah zai wad&atilde;tar da k&otilde;wanne daga yalwarSa. Kuma Allah Y&atilde; kasance Mayalwaci, Mai hikima.';
$t[131] = 'Kuma Allah ne da mulkin abin da ke cikin sammai da abin da ke cikin ƙasa. Kuma lalle ne, haƙĩƙa, Mun yi wasiyya ga waɗanda aka bai wa Litt&atilde;fi a gab&atilde;ninku, da kũ, cẽwa ku bi Allah da taƙawa, kuma idan kun k&atilde;firta, to, lalle ne, Allah Yan&atilde; da abin da yake cikin sammai da abin da yake cikin ƙasa. Kuma Allah Y&atilde; kasance wad&atilde;tacce, G&otilde;dadde.';
$t[132] = 'Kuma Allah ne da mulkin abin da yake cikin sammai da abin da yake cikin ƙasa, kuma Allah Y&atilde; isa Ya zama wakĩli.';
$t[133] = 'Idan Y&atilde; so, z&atilde; Ya tafi da ku, y&atilde; kũ mut&atilde;ne! kuma Ya zo da wasu. Allah Y&atilde; kasance a kan haka, Mai ĩkon yi ne.';
$t[134] = 'Wanda ya kasance Yan&atilde; nufin sakamakon dũniya, to, a wurin Allah sakamakon dũniya da L&atilde;hira yake. Kuma Allah Y&atilde; kasance Mai ji, Mai gani.';
$t[135] = 'Y&atilde; ku waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni! Ku kasance m&atilde;su tsayuwa da &atilde;dalci, m&atilde;su shaida sab&otilde;da Allah, kuma k&otilde; d&atilde; a kanku ne k&otilde; kuwa, mahaifa da mafi kusantar zumunta, ko (wanda ake yi wa shaida k&otilde; a kansa) ya kasance mawad&atilde;ci k&otilde; matalauci, to, Allah ne Mafi cancanta da al\'amarinsu. Sab&otilde;da haka, kada ku bĩbiyi son zũciya, har ku karkata. Kuma idan kuka karkatar da magana, k&otilde; kuwa kuka kau da kai, to lalle ne Allah Y&atilde; kasance Masani ga abin da kuke aikat&atilde;wa.';
$t[136] = 'Y&atilde; kũ waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni! Ku yi ĩm&atilde;ni da Allah da Manzonsa, da Litt&atilde;fin da Ya sassaukar ga ManzonSa da Litt&atilde;fin nan wanda Ya saukar daga gab&atilde;ni. To, wanda ya k&atilde;firta da Allah da mal&atilde;\'ikunSa, da LittattafanSa, da ManzanninSa, da R&atilde;nar L&atilde;hira, to, lalle ne y&atilde; ɓace, ɓata mai nĩsa.';
$t[137] = 'Lalle ne waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni, sa\'an nan kuma suka k&atilde;firta, sa\'an nan kuma suka yi ĩmani, sa\'an nan kuma suka k&atilde;firta sa\'an nan kuma suka ƙ&atilde;ra k&atilde;firci, Allah bai kasance Yan&atilde; g&atilde;farta musu ba, kuma b&atilde; zai shiryar da su ga hanya ba.';
$t[138] = 'Ka yi wa mun&atilde;fukai bush&atilde;ra da cẽwa lalle ne sun&atilde; da az&atilde;ba mai raɗaɗi.';
$t[139] = 'Waɗanda suke riƙon k&atilde;firai mas&otilde;ya, baicin mũminai. Shin sun&atilde; nẽman izza ne a wurinsu? To, lalle ne izza ga Allah take gab&atilde; ɗaya.';
$t[140] = 'Kuma lalle ne Y&atilde; sassaukar muku a cikin Litt&atilde;fi cẽwa idan kun ji &atilde;y&otilde;yin Allah, an&atilde; k&atilde;firta da su, kuma an&atilde; izgili da su, to, kada ku zauna t&atilde;re da sũ, sai sun shiga cikin wani l&atilde;b&atilde;ri. Lalle ne kũ, a l&otilde;kacin nan mis&atilde;linsu kuke. Lalle ne, Allah Mai t&atilde;ra mun&atilde;fukai da k&atilde;firai ne a cikin Jahannama gab&atilde; ɗaya.';
$t[141] = 'Waɗanda suke jiran d&atilde;ko game da ku; har idan wata nasara daga Allah ta kasance a gare ku, sai su ce: &quot;Ashe, ba mu kasance t&atilde;re da kũ ba?&quot; Kuma idan wani rabo ya s&atilde;mu ga k&atilde;firai sai su ce: &quot;Ashe ba mu rinj&atilde;ye ku ba, kuma muka tsare ku daga mũminai?&quot; To, Allah ne Yake yin hukunci tsak&atilde;ninku a R&atilde;nar &iexcl;iy&atilde;ma, kuma Allah b&atilde; zai sanya hanya ba ga k&atilde;firai a kan mũminai.';
$t[142] = 'Lalle ne mun&atilde;fukai sun&atilde; yaudarẽwa da Allah, alh&atilde;li kuwa Shi ne mai yaudarasu; kuma idan sun t&atilde;shi zuwa ga salla, sai su t&atilde;shi sun&atilde; m&atilde;su kas&atilde;la. Suna nũnawa mut&atilde;ne, kuma ba su ambatar Allah sai kaɗan.';
$t[143] = 'M&atilde;su kai-kawo ne a tsak&atilde;nin wancan; b&atilde; zuwa ga waɗannan ba, kuma b&atilde; zuwa ga waɗannan ba. Kuma wanda Allah Ya ɓatar, to, b&atilde; za ka s&atilde;mar masa wata hanya ba.';
$t[144] = 'Y&atilde; ku waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni! Kada ku riƙi k&atilde;firai mas&otilde;ya, baicin mũminai. Shin, kan&atilde; nufin ku sany&atilde; wa Allah dalĩli bayyananne a kanku?';
$t[145] = 'Lalle ne, man&atilde;fukai sun&atilde; a magangara mafi ƙasƙanci daga wuta. Kuma b&atilde; z&atilde; ka s&atilde;ma musu mataimaki ba.';
$t[146] = 'Sai waɗanda suka tũba, kuma suka gy&atilde;ra, kuma suka nẽmi fakuwa ga Allah, kuma suka tsarkake addininsu d&otilde;min Allah, to, waɗannan sun&atilde; t&atilde;re da mũminai, kuma Allah zai bai wa mũminai l&atilde;da mai girma.';
$t[147] = 'Mẽne ne Allah zai amf&atilde;na da yi maku az&atilde;ba idan kun g&otilde;de, kuma kun yi ĩm&atilde;ni? Allah Y&atilde; ksance Mai g&otilde;diya Masani.';
$t[148] = 'Allah b&atilde; Ya son bayyan&atilde;wa da mũn&atilde;na daga magana f&atilde;ce ga wanda aka z&atilde;lunta. Kuma Allah Y&atilde; kasance Mai ji, Masani.';
$t[149] = 'Idan kun bayyana alhẽri, k&otilde; kuwa kuka ɓ&otilde;ye shi, k&otilde; kuwa kuka y&atilde;fe laifi daga cũta, to, lalle ne Allah Y&atilde; kasance Mai y&atilde;fewa, Mai ikon yi.';
$t[150] = 'Lalle ne, waɗanda uke k&atilde;firta da Allah da ManzonSa kuma sun&atilde; nufin su rarrabe a tsak&atilde;nin Allah da manzanninSa, kuma sun&atilde; cẽwa: &quot;Mun&atilde; ĩm&atilde;ni da s&atilde;she, kuma mun&atilde; k&atilde;firta da s&atilde;she.&quot; Kuma sun&atilde; nufin su riƙi hanya a tsak&atilde;nin wannan.';
$t[151] = 'Waɗannan sũ ne k&atilde;firai s&otilde;sai, kuma Mun yi tattali, d&otilde;min k&atilde;firai, az&atilde;ba mai wal&atilde;kantarwa.';
$t[152] = 'Kuma waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni da Allah da manzanninSa, kuma ba su rarrabe a tsak&atilde;nin k&otilde;wa ba daga gare su, waɗannan z&atilde; Mu b&atilde; su ij&atilde;r&otilde;rinsu, kuma Allah Y&atilde; kasance Mai g&atilde;fara, Mai jin ƙai.';
$t[153] = 'Mut&atilde;nen Litt&atilde;fi sun&atilde; tambayar ka ka saukar da wani litt&atilde;fi daga sama, a kansu, to, lalle ne sun tambayi Mũs&atilde; mũf&atilde; girma daga wannan, suka ce: &quot;Ka nũna mana Allah bayyane.&quot; Sai ts&atilde;wa ta k&atilde;m&atilde; su sab&otilde;da z&atilde;luncinsu, sa\'an nan kuma suka riƙi maraƙi (abin baut&atilde;wa) b&atilde;yan hujjoji bayyanannu sun je musu. Sa\'an nan Muka y&atilde;fe laifi daga wancan. Kuma Mun bai wa Mũs&atilde; dalĩli bayyananne.';
$t[154] = 'Kuma Muka ɗaukaka dũtse s&atilde;ma da su, sab&otilde;da alkawarinsu, kuma Muka ce musu: &quot;Ku shiga ƙ&otilde;far kun&atilde; m&atilde;su taw&atilde;li\'u,&quot; Kuma Muka ce musu: &quot;Kada ku ƙẽtare haddi a cikin Asabat,&quot; kuma Muka riƙi alkawari mai kauri daga gare su.&quot;';
$t[155] = 'To, sab&otilde;da warwarẽwarsu ga alkawarinsu, da k&atilde;firtarsu da &atilde;y&otilde;yin Allah, da kisansu ga Annab&atilde;wa, b&atilde; da hakki ba, da maganarsu: &quot;Zuk&atilde;tanmu sun&atilde; cikin rufi.&quot; &Atilde;\'a, Allah ne Ya yunƙe a kansu sab&otilde;da k&atilde;fircinsu, sab&otilde;da haka b&atilde; z&atilde; su yi ĩm&atilde;ni ba f&atilde;ce kaɗan.';
$t[156] = 'Kuma sab&otilde;da k&atilde;fircinsu da faɗarsu, a kan Maryama, ƙiren ƙarya mai girma.';
$t[157] = 'Da faɗarsu: &quot;Lalle ne mu, mun kashe Masĩhu ĩs&atilde; ɗan Maryama Manzon Allah,&quot; alh&atilde;li kuwa ba su kashe shi ba, kuma ba su kẽre shi ba, kuma ammaan kamanta shi ne a garẽ su. Lalle ne waɗanda sauka s&atilde;ɓ&atilde; wa jũna a cikin sha\'aninsa lalle ne, sun&atilde; shakka daga gare, shi, b&atilde; da wani ilmi f&atilde;ce bin zato kuma ba su kashe shi ba bisa ga yaƙĩni.';
$t[158] = '&Atilde;\'a, Allah Ya ɗauke shi zuwa garẽ Shi, kuma Allah Y&atilde; kasance Mabuw&atilde;yi, Mai hikima.';
$t[159] = 'Kuma b&atilde;bu k&otilde;wa daga Mut&atilde;nen Littafi, f&atilde;ce lalle yan&atilde; ĩm&atilde;ni da shi a gab&atilde;nin mutuwarsa, kuma a R&atilde;nar &iexcl;iy&atilde;ma yana kasancẽwa mai shaida, a kansu.';
$t[160] = 'To, sab&otilde;da z&atilde;lunci daga waɗanda suka tũba (Yahũdu) Muka haramta musu abũbuwa masu d&atilde;ɗi waɗanda aka halatta su a gare su, kuma sab&otilde;da taushẽwarsu daga hanyar Allah da yawa.';
$t[161] = 'Da karɓarsu ga riba, alh&atilde;li kuwa an hana su daga gare ta, da cin su ga dũkiyar mut&atilde;ne daƙarya. Kuma Muka yi tattali, d&otilde;min k&atilde;firai, az&atilde;ba mai raɗaɗi.';
$t[162] = 'Amma tabbatattu a cikin ilmi daga gare su, da mũminai, suna ĩmani da abin da aka saukar zuwa gare ka, da abin da aka saukar daga gab&atilde;ninka, madalla da masu tsai da salla, da m&atilde;su b&atilde;yar da zakka, da m&atilde;su ĩm&atilde;ni daAllah da R&atilde;nar L&atilde;hira. Waɗannan z&atilde; Mu b&atilde; su l&atilde;da mai girma.';
$t[163] = 'Lalle ne Mu, Mun yi wahayi zuwa gare ka, kamar yadda Muka yi wahayi zuwa ga Nũhu da annab&atilde;wa daga b&atilde;yansa. Kuma Mun yi wahayi zuwa ga Ibr&atilde;hĩma da Ism&atilde;\'ĩla da Is\'h&atilde;ƙa da Yaƙũbu da jĩk&otilde;ki da ĩsa da Ayũba da Yũnusa da H&atilde;runa da Sulaim&atilde;n. Kuma Mun bai wa D&atilde;wũda zabũra.';
$t[164] = 'Da wasu Manzanni, haƙĩ ƙa, Mun b&atilde; da l&atilde;barinsu a gare ka daga gab&atilde;ni, da wasu manzanni waɗanda ba Mu b&atilde; da l&atilde;b&atilde;rinsu ba a gare ka, kuma Allah Y&atilde; yi magana da Mũs&atilde;, magana s&otilde;sai.';
$t[165] = 'Manzanni m&atilde;su b&atilde;yar da bush&atilde;ra kuma m&atilde;su gargaɗi d&otilde;min kada wata hujja ta kasance ga mut&atilde;ne a kan Allah b&atilde;yan Manzannin. Kuma Allah y&atilde; kasance Mabuw&atilde;yi, Mai hikima.';
$t[166] = 'Amma Allah Yan&atilde; shaida da abin da Ya saukar zuwa gare ka. Y&atilde; saukar da shi da saninSa. Kuma mal&atilde;\'iku sun&atilde; shaida. Kuma Allah Y&atilde; isa Ya zama shaida.';
$t[167] = 'Lalle ne, waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta kuma suka kange (wasu mut&atilde;ne) daga hanyar Allah, haƙĩƙa, sun ɓace, ɓata mai nĩsa.';
$t[168] = 'Lalle ne waɗanda suka k&atilde;firta, kuma suka yi z&atilde;lunci, Allah bai kasance Yana yi musu g&atilde;fara ba, kuma b&atilde; Ya shiryar da su ga hanya.';
$t[169] = 'F&atilde;ce hanyar Jahannama, sun&atilde; m&atilde;su dawwama a cikinta har abada, kuma wannan y&atilde; kasance, ga Allah, mai sauƙi.';
$t[170] = 'Y&atilde; kũ mut&atilde;ne! Haƙĩƙa, Manzo y&atilde; je muku da gaskiya daga Ubangijinku. Sab&otilde;da haka ku yi ĩm&atilde;ni y&atilde; fi zama alhẽri a gare ku. Kuma idan kun k&atilde;firta, to, Allah Yan&atilde; da abin da ke cikin sammai da ƙasa. Kuma Allah Y&atilde; kasance Masani, Mai hikima.';
$t[171] = 'Y&atilde; Mut&atilde;nen Litt&atilde;fi! Kada ku zurfaf&atilde; a cikin addininku. Kuma kada ku faɗa, ga Allah, f&atilde;ce gaskiya. Abin da aka sani kawai, Masĩ hu ĩsa ɗan Maryama Manzon Allah ne, kuma kalmarSa, y&atilde; jẽfa ta zuwa ga Maryama, kuma rũhi ne daga gare Shi. Sab&otilde;da haka, ku yi ĩm&atilde;ni da Allah da manzanninSa, kuma kada ku ce, &quot;Uku&quot;. Ku hanu (daga faɗin haka) y&atilde; fi zama alhẽri a gare ku. Abin da aka sani kawai, Allah Ubangiji ne Guda. TsarkinSa y&atilde; tabbata daga wani abin haifuwa ya kasance a gare Shi! Shĩ ne da abin da ke cikin sammai da abin da ke cikin ƙasa kuma Allah Y&atilde; isa Ya zama wakĩli.';
$t[172] = 'Masĩhu b&atilde; ya ƙy&atilde;mar ya kasance b&atilde;wa ga Allah, kuma haka mal&atilde;\'ikun nan makusanta. Kuma wanda ya yi ƙy&atilde;mar bautarSa kuma yi yi girman kai, to, zai t&atilde;ra su zuwa gare shi gab&atilde; ɗaya.';
$t[173] = 'To, amma waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni, kuma suka aikata ayyukan ƙwaiai, to z&atilde; Ya cika musu ij&atilde;r&otilde;rinsu, kuma Yan&atilde; ƙ&atilde;ra musu daga falalarSa. Kuma amma waɗanda suka yi ƙy&atilde;ma, kuma suka yi girman kai, to, z&atilde; Ya yi musu az&atilde;ba, az&atilde;ba mai raɗɗi kuma b&atilde; su samun wani mas&otilde;yi d&otilde;min kansu, baicin Allah, kuma b&atilde; su samun mataimaki.';
$t[174] = 'Y&atilde; kũ mut&atilde;ne! Haƙĩƙa wani dalĩli daga Ubangijinku y&atilde; je muku kuma Mun saukar da wani haske, bayyananne zuwa gare ku.';
$t[175] = 'To, amma waɗanda suka yi ĩm&atilde;ni da Allah kuma suka faku a gare Shi, to, zai shigar da su cikin wata rahama daga gare Shi da wata falala, kuma Ya shiryar da su zuwa gare Shi ga tafarki madaidaici.';
$t[176] = 'Sun&atilde; yi maka fatawa. Ka ce: &quot;Allah Yan&atilde; bayyana muku fatawa a cikin \'Kal&atilde;la.&quot;\' Idan mutum ya halaka, ba shi da, rẽshe kuma yana da \'yar\'uwa, to, tana da rabin abin da ya bari, kuma shi yana g&atilde;don ta, idan wani rẽshe bai kasance ba a gare ta. Sa\'an nan idan (\'yan\'uwa m&atilde;t&atilde;) suka kasance biyu, to suna da kashi biyu daga kashi uku ɗin abin da ya bari. Kuma idan sun kasance, \'yan\'uwa, maza da m&atilde;t&atilde; to namiji yana da mis&atilde;lin rabon m&atilde;t&atilde; biyu. Allah Yana bayyanawa a gare ku, d&otilde;min kada ku ɓace. Kuma Allah ne, Masani ga dukan k&otilde;me.';
?>